'''Dylan Lewis''' is an Australian television and radio personality who appeared in an uncredited performance as a patron in [[Dex's Diner/Legends|Dex's Diner]] in [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Attack of the Clones'']]. He acted as the Human wearing the helmet sitting directly behind [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]], conversing with [[Honka]] and [[Sidewa]].

Lewis is known as a Star Wars fan, and appeared in ''The Phandom Menace'', a documentary on Australia's obsession with Star Wars.

